name: Why I Love Flying With CENTRAL MOUNTAIN AIR | Dornier 328 Edmonton to Calgary
description:
Central Mountain Air, or CMA for short, is a western Canadian airline that flies mostly within British Columbia, but they also have a few routes here in Alberta.

If you recall from last year, I’ve already flown with Central Mountain Air, doing the reverse of this flight from Edmonton to Calgary

Well, as it turns out, that video from last year would be a big part of today’s flight...
